title: Bastille 2016-06-10 Pinkpop Holland
description:
Here is a nice Pinkpop broadcast. Chech my account for more Pinkpop broadcasts.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Bastille
Pinkpop, Megaland, Landgraaf, The Netherlands
June 10, 2016
Main Stage 18:25-19:25

Setlist (from setlist.fm):
01. Bad Blood
02. Things We Lost in the Fire
03. Send Them Off
04. Weight of Living, Pt. II
05. Overjoyed
06. The Currents
07. These Streets
08. Laura Palmer
09. Oblivion
10. Snakes
11. Flaws
12. Lesser Of 2 Evils / Hello
13. Icarus
14. Of the Night
15. Pompeii

Taken from the Dutch national television channel NPO Cultura broadcast, June 10, 2016.

The original broadcast had some flaws soundwise. The replay after midnight and the next morning had that corrected, but was missing a total of 20 minutes compared to the original broadcast.
I have combined both broadcasts into this version. The part between approx. 23:50 and 30:30 comes from the 2nd broadcast. This corrects the mentioned flaws.

Lineage : NPO Cultura DVB-C - Humax iHDR-5050C - VideoReDo TVSuite 4.20.7.629
